rows.label: tlk70000074_05_msg0001
rows.name:
In the annals of House Horrison, there's
no record of a change like this ever
happening in the history of Iira...

rows.label: tlk70000074_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Now, as head of the house, I plan to
diligently record these events, so that
future generations may know of them.

rows.label: tlk70000074_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I believe those of us living here in
Superbia have a duty to future
generations to carry this out.

rows.label: tlk70000074_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Please leave things to us here, Your
Majesty. We would not distract you
from your mission.
